    \ingroup STRUCTS /** \struct CUVIDSOURCEPARAMS /** Describes parameters needed in cuvidCreateVideoSource API /** NVDECODE API is intended for HW accelerated video decoding so CUvideosource doesn't have audio demuxer for all supported /** containers. It's recommended to clients to use their own or third party demuxer if audio support is needed. /
